This is a basic system service that manages charging, discharging, app launch, and device temperature control. To provide services for you, this service needs to access the network to update the authentication status so as to better ensure charging security. It also needs to read the app list to control battery temperature so as to prevent the device from heating up easily and to extend battery life.\nThe permissions required by battery service cannot be turned off, as doing so could cause overheating or charging issues.
